  </p>

</div><!-- end main-col -->

<div class="span-5 append-3 last"><!-- inner-right-col -->
  <p class="huge-text">3</p>
  <p>
    Gossamer completed the analysis, setup and migration of their hosting in
    under three days.
  </p>
  <hr />

